Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:06.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗音  輪盤選擇了你和讓治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:10.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝解放之日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  紗音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看出你的嘴邊充滿著留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓讓治教你女人的快感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為連初夜都沒經歷就要被殺死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿是留戀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:33.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點忘了  你也是金藏的優秀傢俱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:38.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓嘉音君的屍體消失還損害了他的名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:44.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  紗音  你在生這個氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再讓你們見一次面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很愉快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓生離死別的人們再次相會無論何時都是很愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  嘉音  陪他們玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一而再再而三地玷污死者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:09.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:17.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓治  請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想移動中心軸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:35.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  靈鏡借給你力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說傢俱真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:43.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像不小心腳趾頭撞到了衣櫃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:50.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是傢俱  並且我認為此刻的你非常可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:51.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛的兩人不可能沒有留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:04:00.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們卻沒有你所期待的一點點留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還講道理  你這傢俱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於相愛的兩人來說身體的交融一定有其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:11.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那與你所說的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它賦有神聖的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:20.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和讓治發誓永遠相愛  作為證明而接受了戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經完成了永恆的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已無任何留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說漂亮話  你這傢俱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會失望的  你只要看過一次身後那眼鏡男的骯髒慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊算了  少廢話  你這傢俱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  你這破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓治  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  紗音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了我挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是這樣我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓治  我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後請讓我聽你說愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:31.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  紗代  我永遠都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你聽嗎  白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓座夫人  我是源次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:02.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現南條醫生和熊澤的屍體了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  現在就去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是被日本刀之類的東西砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第七夜  剜膝殺之」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第八夜  剜足殺之」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這樣的話就少了第四到第六夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次先生  讓治哥他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說要去夏妃夫人的房間裡找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是兩三小時之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門被鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人君  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:07.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓治哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察到來之前不能亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果然是第四到第六夜的再現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來直到第八夜為止就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九夜是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:56.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第九夜  魔女復甦  無人生還」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我們將要死去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…  別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  源次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有事請隨時吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下竟然置源次先生於不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓座伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K200\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}碑文之謎進展如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K200\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}時限馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K240\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}第九夜即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:10.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  你到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:16.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人君  我斷定你是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:20.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會被懷疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:25.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外沒人會放下這封信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要無法證明你的清白你就是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  要說我可疑的話你也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:36.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我注意到偷偷地放下了信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來也可以懷疑你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是狼早就開槍射殺你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不算理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  樓座伯母一開始就很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加親族會議的大人們被殺了六人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有樓座伯母不在那禮拜堂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伯母把老爸他們召集到那裡並殺害了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就全都能說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不壞  戰人和媽媽都不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是魔女用魔法幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是魔女  是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  現身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:39.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我們宣佈全都是自己用魔法幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:53.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能再次看見你的微笑  我就死而無憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我思慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:02.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我向你道一聲歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:30.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  門沒鎖  要進來就進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是源次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是時候讓您知道一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:44.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請直接聽館主大人他們向您說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館主大人  我把他帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:17.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的好  右代宮戰人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有事要問我不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往黃金鄉的大門即將開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你要問多少問題我都會回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會發生這樣的事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室的鑰匙呢？魔女的真面目呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把我叫到這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都給我解釋清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  只是有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能接受我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時就給我跪下  親吻我的靴尖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:05.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了讓你屈服才把你叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要能讓我接受的話吻靴子什麼的叫我做什麼我都做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先從哪個問題開始回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全部回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起碼拿走一條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能見到貝亞特麗切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黃金鄉就能見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧？趕快現身吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜已完成了復甦的我們黃金鄉的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切卿到場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  貝倫卡斯特爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  你還喜歡我的傢俱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不得的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜諸位為我歡聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完結和起始的指針將重合於一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:55.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟黃金之門！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:16.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝亞特麗切  現在就讓我去黃金鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我跪下  表示你的敬意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我貼緊地面  顯露你的卑微吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼前你們敢碰真里亞一根手指頭試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你們認識到  原來身處的地獄還根本算不上地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  幫忙裝彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你們見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金之夢是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  子彈裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  即使媽媽這麼壞  還願意和媽媽在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和媽媽在一起最好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真里亞的  唯一的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金什麼的根本就用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要牽著你的手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個多麼愚蠢的媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所期望的東西我都可以給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為給你那超強運氣的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的痛楚是來自於兄弟姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就送給你報復他們的喜悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:43.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲食佔人們快樂中的很大一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開始美食之宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這杯是餐前酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:54.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取名的話就是血腥藏臼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是把那個一直耀武揚威的藏臼大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:02.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠地擰乾之後搾出來的鮮血之酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盤是用正當時下的蔬菜調配而成的舌片沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:16.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用你在九歲生日時就想咬碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪羽的舌頭所製作的你期望已久的沙拉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一盤是用一直出賣你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:27.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留弗夫的臉皮包的鱸魚派
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點是你一直假裝疼愛的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:42.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  真里亞的存在是不是一個障礙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:48.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽往家裡面帶男人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男人在外面過夜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞總是給你添麻煩  製造障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生下來  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把真里亞吃了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞為了媽媽變成了美味的烤蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:11.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己女兒做成的烤蘋果  真是最棒的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養育了這麼一個好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是最厲害的母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宮樓座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你對我的款待還滿意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就承認我的存在吧  承認我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宮樓座  承認貝亞特麗切是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡耍小聰明的戰人已經屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似挺好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為我露一手  把你的奶子切成肉片做個三明治給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰…戰人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是成為傢俱連靈魂都已經屈服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:02.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  要說把自己吃掉之類的話還早了十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  過了十年一定要跟我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:06.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是決不能屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了樓座伯母堅持到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再一次有了戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種  我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受你的挑戰  右代宮戰人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就否定我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  這一盤的遊戲玩的開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一邊倒的單方面遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「貝倫卡斯特爾卿沒有勝算」是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:47.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝算？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用裝糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是旁觀者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:07.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然能獲得和那個最強的魔女貝倫卡斯特爾卿對戰的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了  貝倫卡斯特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也閒得慌呢  拉姆達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自把別人的名字省略成拉姆達啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我告訴她你正和我對立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:26.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆達德爾塔卿就說她要站到和你對立的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在記仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是和你作對的人不論是誰我都視為同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愛怎麼樣就怎麼樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然露餡了我也乾脆認真來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就下盤遊戲見吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:20.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亞  真里亞  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:22.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我這個壞媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再打你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:28.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:33.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋葉原站不認識的哥哥給的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宮樓座小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:40.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被動畫中你的表現一箭穿心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:46.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討人厭的非正常表現  真的很給力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想被你的右腳踐踏  嘿  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體觀眾奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  castling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:10.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得像南瓜糖一樣粉碎的傢伙們  儘管上前
